lead_paragraph: Makayla Epps scored 20 points, Evelyn Akhator had 15 points and 13 rebounds and No. 20 Kentucky defeated Samford 80-57 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Fast Start Propels No. 20 Kentucky Women Past Sanford 80-57
